node.text:
The 2020 Mint 400 was our last hurrah before the world crisis forced everyone to hit pause. It was a party in the desert in so many ways: The Top 2 overall in the premier Unlimited Truck class, 29 class podium spots, 13 class wins, a Class 10 podium sweep, a Top 4 in UTV Pro Turbo, and Top 2 in the National Hare & Hound Motorcycle Race Hooligan Open Class. Most importantly, though, was our eighth consecutive year of FOX overall domination in the Unlimited Truck class, courtesy of Luke McMillin.
// #ridefox #offroad

At 2019 Mint 400, FOX-equipped vehicles won in 11 different classes and @justinlofton41 made history by being the first 3-time overall winner.

The 2020 Mint 400 will feature 4 laps of brutal Nevada desert, including the roughest section of course - the FOX Proving Grounds. Festivities begin this Wednesday, March 4th, with the vehicle parade down Las Vegas Blvd. Stay tuned for live updates and fresh content throughout the week!
.
.
.
Race: @TheMint400
// #ridefox #offroad #Mint400
